briefdescription.para: This function indicates a received I-PDU from a lower layer communication interface module.

simplesect.para: Check if the socket route is enabled.
The I-PDU data is copied from the underlying layer to LdCom.

parameterdescription.para: Contains the length (SduLength) of the received I-PDU and a pointer to a buffer (SduDataPtr) containing the I-PDU.

simplesect.title: Input->Output-Correlation
simplesect.para: Input include the id of the received Com I-PDU and payload buffer. Respective service handle callbacks are called if the protocol version match.
